{"lemma":"فالِقِ","slug":"فالِقِ","root":"ف.ل.ق","root_slug":"ف-ل-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ل-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فالِق","root":"فلق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34554"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34554","headword_ar":"فَالِقٌ","root":"flq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Splitting, cleaving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dividing lengthwise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAliqu A@loHab~i waA@ln~awaY","text_ar":"فَالِقُ ا@لْحَبِّ وَا@لنَّوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, *) in the Kur [vi. 95], (O,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Cleaver of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"dry"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grain"},{"kind":"text","text":"so as to produce therefrom green leaves ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the date-stone"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Creator thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. *) And hence the saying of Áïsheh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a AlbukaA='a faAliqN kabidiY","text_ar":"اـِنَّ البُكَا=ءَ فَالِقٌ كَبِدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily weeping is cleaving my liver"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, also, in the Kur [vi. 96],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAliqN AlA_iSobaAHi","text_ar":"فَالِقٌ الاـِصْبَاحِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who causeth the dawn to break: in"},{"kind":"text","text":"which instance, also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fAlq","text_ar":"فالق"},{"kind":"text","text":"has reference to the meaning of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Creator:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) so says Zj. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxolapN faAliqN","text_ar":"نَخْلَةٌ فَالِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A palmtree splitting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cleaving from"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to disclose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the spathe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuloqN","text_ar":"فُلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfawaAliqu","text_ar":"الفَوَالِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaAliqu","text_ar":"الفَالِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The veins that divide"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to form ramifying veins"},{"kind":"text","text":"(thus I render ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuruwqu Almutafal~iqapu","text_ar":"العُرُوقُ المُتَفَلِّقَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":")]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the human being."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faloqN","text_ar":"فَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence. ―         -b6-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaqN","text_ar":"فَلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", former half, in three places. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwarikapi","text_ar":"الوَرِكَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xal~ayotuhu bifaAliqapi","text_ar":"خَلَّيْتُهُ بِفَالِقَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, as in the T,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifaAliqi AlwrkA='","text_ar":"بِفَالِقِ الوركا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", [thus in the TA, but I think that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrkp","text_ar":"الوركة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwrkA='","text_ar":"الوركا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"are evidently mistran-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2443},{"kind":"text","text":"scriptions, and that the right reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwadokaA='i","text_ar":"الوَدْكَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dAl","text_ar":"دال"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I left him in the low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, tract in the midst of"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the sand [called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Wedkà"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}